{"tid":766434,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧麗欣IG突然大清洗只追蹤王子一個　好姊妹全部冇份！","createTime":"2018-08-03T14:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T18:00:07.000Z","uid":147522,"like":46,"dislike":286,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d6376e059a8c19dd16d3023263e9ffc6a950e5","tid":766434,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"Stephy鄧麗欣與棒棒堂前成員王子邱勝翊公開認愛之後，事件曾引起網民熱烈討論。Stephy更帶王子讓好友杜汶澤認識，杜汶澤更對男方讚不絕口。兩人正處於非常甜蜜的熱戀期，而Stephy近日一個小舉動，閃爆網民對眼囉。<br />\n<br />\n她早前將IG的Follower進行大清洗，最後只追蹤了3個帳戶。她的Cookies好姊妹如吳雨霏、楊愛瑾等人都不在名單之上，Stephy似是戀愛大過天，就連朋友都不要！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/225419_1c431bb47cdabcf7aa2e159705fd9a0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F225419_1c431bb47cdabcf7aa2e159705fd9a0b.png&h=81db4232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反王子就未有任何舉動，不過可以證明就是Stephy似乎好鍾意王子囉～"},{"pid":"bb8bb7ccde2eea2da0d1f41122dd39a3069affd9","tid":766434,"uid":31675,"like":389,"dislike":1,"score":388,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"万刀甲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c902239587db7fe0734660d2cec4349e939d13","tid":766434,"uid":76063,"like":604,"dislike":15,"score":589,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"Stephy似乎好鍾意王子囉～<br />\n<br />\n驚嫁唔出嘛"},{"pid":"0eae3bac7c5ac9c59351076440169a8a59843a10","tid":766434,"uid":129660,"like":394,"dislike":9,"score":385,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n隻mk鴨有咩咁吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39ac42b053c293414dbd068de5704dd42b197f8","tid":766434,"uid":555,"like":45,"dislike":10,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"g搏上新聞啫"},{"pid":"a377dc6d8b4370ee4e280d8d2e620c97dda4c3fd","tid":766434,"uid":195009,"like":63,"dislike":3,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"小方<img src=\"/asse